  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/01f46184ca3ed0e56b5dae1480de8c66.avif?t=1728316026\" width=574 height=121 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>It's so hot outside, let's cool a little!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SQUARE WORD is now available on Steam with the SUMMER EDITION!</h2><br><strong>COCO, the funny parrot,</strong> will be your guide in this new edition! Chill and relax!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/135518b6d524441c49297fc37231f4e6.webp?t=1728316026\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Four summer themes: <strong>Beach - Vacation - Camping - Ocean</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/135518b6d524441c49297fc37231f4e6.webp?t=1728316026\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 140+ words to find.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/135518b6d524441c49297fc37231f4e6.webp?t=1728316026\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Handcrafted grids, I tried to make words association in the grid.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/135518b6d524441c49297fc37231f4e6.webp?t=1728316026\" width=13 height=13 /></span> Daily challenge.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/extras/135518b6d524441c49297fc37231f4e6.webp?t=1728316026\" width=13 height=13 /></span> 4 difficulties (easy to very hard).<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1707670/ex